    "description": {
      "value": "<p>You know the @Compendium[5e-complete.5e-spells.5vTIaeOwSclMzCoU]{Shape Water} cantrip. When you reach 3rd level, you can cast the @Compendium[5e-complete.5e-spells.PbQvcZ70QhVM8dOy]{Create or Destroy Water} spell as a 2nd-level spell once with this trait, and you regain the ability to cast it this way when you finish a long rest. Constitution is your spellcasting ability for these spells.</p>\n<p><em style=\"box-sizing:border-box;user-select:text;color:#191813;font-size:13px\">Note. Once you reach 3rd level, go into Details and set this ability to have 1 use per Long Rest.</em></p>",
